info.name: Api Documentation
info.description:
# Introduction
Api Documentation for car rental REST API with JWT Authorization

# Overview
To use API with admin or user authentication you have to put generated token from "/login" endpoint
to your request header with Key "Authorization" and Value "Bearer XXXX".

# Authentication  
The preffered way of using API is simply use with Swagger(baseUrl/swagger-ui/), Postman  or even browser.

# Error Codes
REST API informs you with appropriate response code with described errors.

# Rate Limit
API haven't specified limit to the number of requests an user can send.
